        "content": "<p>It's semisimple.  I'm working over R and looking at a specific real form of E6, but it's still semisimple.  As I tried to explain <a href=\"https://golem.ph.utexas.edu/category/2020/11/octonions_and_the_standard_mod_9.html#c058895\">on the n-Category Cafe</a>, I'm building it by gluing together two semidirect products.</p>",
